---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.jsx';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="About Mehdi Bamou - Enterprise Architect & Technology Leader"
  description="Learn about Mehdi Bamou's journey in enterprise architecture, digital transformation, and bridging technology innovation between Morocco and Europe."
  path="/about"
>
  <Hero 
    title="About Me"
    subtitle="Bridging Technology Innovation Between Morocco and Europe"
    client:load
  />

  <section class="section-spacing">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
        <!-- Headshot -->
        <div class="md:col-span-1">
          <div class="sticky top-24">
            <div class="w-full aspect-square bg-primary rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white text-6xl font-bold shadow-xl">
              MB
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-12">
          <!-- Professional Journey -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold mb-6 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
              Professional Journey
            </h2>
            <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
              <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
                With over 15 years of experience in enterprise architecture and digital transformation, 
                I've had the privilege of working with organizations across Europe and the MENA region, 
                helping them navigate the complexities of modern technology landscapes.
              </p>
              <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
                Currently based in DÃ¼sseldorf, Germany, I specialize in designing scalable enterprise 
                architectures, developing cloud strategies, and leading digital transformation initiatives 
                that drive real business value. My unique position allows me to bridge technological 
                innovation between European markets and the rapidly evolving MENA technology ecosystem.
              </p>
              <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
                I believe in architecture that serves people, not the other way around. My approach 
                combines technical excellence with a deep understanding of business objectives, cultural 
                contexts, and the human elements that make or break digital transformation efforts.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Timeline -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold mb-6 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
              Career Highlights
            </h2>
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="border-l-4 border-primary pl-6">
                <div class="text-sm text-primary font-semibold mb-1">2020 - Present</div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold mb-2 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
                  Senior Enterprise Architect
                </h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
                  Leading enterprise architecture initiatives for multinational organizations, 
                  focusing on cloud transformation and digital innovation strategies.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="border-l-4 border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-600 pl-6">
                <div class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-semibold mb-1">2015 - 2020</div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold mb-2 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
                  Solutions Architect
                </h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
                  Designed and implemented scalable solutions for enterprise clients across 
                  various industries including finance, healthcare, and telecommunications.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="border-l-4 border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-600 pl-6">
                <div class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-semibold mb-1">2010 - 2015</div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold mb-2 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
                  Technical Lead
                </h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
                  Led development teams in building enterprise applications and establishing 
                  best practices for software development and architecture.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Multicultural Background -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold mb-6 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
              Multicultural Perspective
            </h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Born and raised in Morocco, educated and working across Europe, I bring a unique 
              multicultural perspective to technology leadership. This background enables me to:
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
                  Navigate complex cross-cultural business environments with ease
                </span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
                  Bridge technology partnerships between European and MENA markets
                </span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
                  Understand diverse regulatory and business requirements across regions
                </span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
                  Communicate effectively in French, Arabic, English, and German
                </span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Credentials -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold mb-6 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
              Credentials & Education
            </h2>
            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div class="card">
                <div class="text-primary mb-3">
                  <svg class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
                  TOGAF Certified
                </h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 text-sm">
                  The Open Group Architecture Framework certification
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="card">
                <div class="text-primary mb-3">
                  <svg class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
                  Executive MBA
                </h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 text-sm">
                  In Progress - Business Administration & Strategy
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="card">
                <div class="text-primary mb-3">
                  <svg class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 15a4 4 0 004 4h9a5 5 0 10-.1-9.999 5.002 5.002 0 10-9.78 2.096A4.001 4.001 0 003 15z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
                  Cloud Certifications
                </h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 text-sm">
                  AWS Solutions Architect, Azure Architect
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="card">
                <div class="text-primary mb-3">
                  <svg class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
                  M.Sc. Computer Science
                </h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 text-sm">
                  Software Engineering & Architecture
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="section-spacing bg-primary text-white">
    <div class="container-custom text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-bold mb-6">
        Let's Work Together
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto opacity-90">
        Interested in collaborating on enterprise architecture, digital transformation, 
        or exploring opportunities in the MENA market?
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-secondary inline-block">
        Get in Touch
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
